---
author: Jen Carlson
date: Dec 21, 2016 4:15 pm
title: Sarah Jessica Parker Has The Loveliest NYC Instagram Account
---

	
										<p>The images are sometimes peculiarly angled, blurry, grainy, or not very well-lit, but that is part of the charm of <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171101043431/https://www.instagram.com/sarahjessicaparker/">Sarah Jessica Parker&apos;s Instagram</a> feed. The actress&apos;s photos aren&apos;t usually set up and curated like so many &quot;Instagram influencers&quot; out there, she&apos;s just sharing what she sees, oftentimes as a hurried New Yorker... and we really, really appreciate it.</p>

<p>I don&apos;t follow many celebrities on Instagram, but SJP is a must, especially for anyone who has ever felt some sort of poetic love for this beautiful, dirty town. This year I found my mood brightened so many times by her photos &#x2014; which always come with a side of whimsy in the caption &#x2014; that I felt like spreading the joy. If you haven&apos;t followed her yet, do it now. It&apos;s a guaranteed smile for a fleeting moment in your future, and we&apos;re gonna need all of those we can get <a href="gothamist.com/2016/12/19/you_must_make_a_friend_of_horror.php">in 2017</a>. </p>

<p>Thank you, SJP, for sharing your rose-tinted view on the world.</p>
